    "details": {
        "style": "DD0587-002",
        "colorway": "Light Graphite/White/Wolf Grey",
        "retailPrice": 220,
        "releaseDate": "02/28/2026",
        "accessories": "Two Lace Locks",
        "description": "The Air Jordan 5 Retro Wolf Grey (2026) marks the return of a fan-favorite colorway that originally debuted in 2011. Dressed in light graphite, white, and wolf grey, the sneaker delivers a clean, understated look that has aged effortlessly over time.\n\nWhen the Wolf Grey colorway first released, it offered a softer, more versatile alternative to the bolder Jordan 5 designs of the era. That simplicity became its strength, allowing the silhouette to shine without relying on loud contrasts.\n\nThe 2026 retro stays true to that original vision, preserving the look that made it so popular while also including the iconic Nike Air logo on the heel."
    },
